long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a Chrome browser extension that is built to provide you quick and easy access to the private search engine with the same name. We respect your privacy and do not follow your internet footprint or match your personally identifiable information with advertisements. When using our extension by typing the information that you want to look for from your browser’s address bar or from the extension’s UI,  you can still see ads in your result feed but they are not targeted: we do not store your personal information or share them with advertisers. 

By adding this extension to your Chrome browser, you accept and agree to our Privacy Policy and End-User License Agreement.

Privacy Policy: https://www.myprivatesearch.com/extpolicy

EULA: https://www.myprivatesearch.com/terms

Help Center: https://www.myprivatesearch.com/help

Contact Us: https://www.myprivatesearch.com/contact
